{"tid":1830332,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（屯門黃店）轉角","createTime":"2020-01-19T13:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T07:58:41.000Z","uid":21545,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1ea62b930d47f4dccaaea6a5ff8166c5418cff","tid":1830332,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EN9TXyO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEN9TXyO.png&h=edcb7901&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDHBVkw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDHBVkw.jpg&h=1eae3e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日去咗屯門巿廣場行街<br />\n<br />\n決定幫襯一下屯門嘅黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去咗轉角 叫咗一個蒲燒鯛魚飯 送一舊玉子 仲包餐飲<br />\n<br />\n鯛魚夠滑夠香又唔腥 蒲燒汁鹹甜適中 玉子多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺盤又靚 打卡一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n價錢：$68<br />\n<br />\n評分：10/10<br />\n<br />\n總結：溝女自用兩相宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃店prove : 來自和你eat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e917b21a7e0218330bbbe4dc96f2d8712464a0fa","tid":1830332,"uid":233156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d6d37232ba354177f102e3a303c012c1acf0e1","tid":1830332,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:36:28.000Z","msg":"食過，還可以"},{"pid":"3203e5434c9f770e63e28ae47dbb89ee9e939d68","tid":1830332,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score